$ NastAero VM7: Cantilever Plate Strip (CQUAD4)
$ Reference: Euler-Bernoulli cantilever beam theory
$ 1-element wide, 8-element long plate strip along X
$ Length=1.0m (X), Width=0.1m (Y), t=0.01m
$ E=200GPa, nu=0.3, rho=7850 kg/m^3
$
$ 2 rows of 9 nodes = 18 nodes, 8 CQUAD4 elements
$ Row 1 (y=0.0): nodes 1-9, x=0.0 to 1.0 (spacing 0.125m)
$ Row 2 (y=0.1): nodes 10-18, x=0.0 to 1.0
$
$ Fixed at x=0 (nodes 1, 10): all 6 DOFs
$ Tip load at x=1.0 (nodes 9, 18): 50N each in -Z = 100N total
$
$ Analytical (cantilever beam equivalent):
$ D = Et^3/(12(1-nu^2)) = 200e9*(0.01)^3/(12*(1-0.09))
$   = 200e9*1e-6/10.92 = 18315.02 N-m
$ For strip width b=0.1m: EI_eff = D*b = 18315.02*0.1 = 1831.5 N-m^2
$ delta_tip = PL^3/(3*EI_eff)
$           = 100*1.0^3/(3*1831.5)
$           = 100/5494.5
$           = 0.01820 m
$
SOL 101
CEND
TITLE = VM7 - CANTILEVER PLATE STRIP
SPC = 1
LOAD = 1
DISPLACEMENT(PRINT) = ALL
SPCFORCES(PRINT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
$
$ Row 1 (y=0.0): nodes 1-9
GRID,1,,0.0,0.0,0.0
GRID,2,,0.125,0.0,0.0
GRID,3,,0.25,0.0,0.0
GRID,4,,0.375,0.0,0.0
GRID,5,,0.5,0.0,0.0
GRID,6,,0.625,0.0,0.0
GRID,7,,0.75,0.0,0.0
GRID,8,,0.875,0.0,0.0
GRID,9,,1.0,0.0,0.0
$
$ Row 2 (y=0.1): nodes 10-18
GRID,10,,0.0,0.1,0.0
GRID,11,,0.125,0.1,0.0
GRID,12,,0.25,0.1,0.0
GRID,13,,0.375,0.1,0.0
GRID,14,,0.5,0.1,0.0
GRID,15,,0.625,0.1,0.0
GRID,16,,0.75,0.1,0.0
GRID,17,,0.875,0.1,0.0
GRID,18,,1.0,0.1,0.0
$
$ 8 CQUAD4 elements (connectivity: bottom-left, bottom-right, top-right, top-left)
CQUAD4,1,1,1,2,11,10
CQUAD4,2,1,2,3,12,11
CQUAD4,3,1,3,4,13,12
CQUAD4,4,1,4,5,14,13
CQUAD4,5,1,5,6,15,14
CQUAD4,6,1,6,7,16,15
CQUAD4,7,1,7,8,17,16
CQUAD4,8,1,8,9,18,17
$
$ Shell property: t=0.01m
PSHELL,1,1,0.01,1
MAT1,1,200.0e9,,0.3,7850.0
$
$ Fixed at x=0 (left edge: nodes 1 and 10)
SPC1,1,123456,1,10
$
$ Tip forces at x=1.0 (nodes 9 and 18): 50N each in -Z direction
FORCE,1,9,,50.0,0.0,0.0,-1.0
FORCE,1,18,,50.0,0.0,0.0,-1.0
$
